{"h2717dd3dgde44g45f8g839dg51057cc5e524": ["I'll talk to the guards in Baldur's Gate. I speak their language.", "dd9178e7-1e3f-43bc-8a38-666dfcac7d0c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "b3972089-a213-15a4-d121-672dbc7c07bb"], "h1a23fe5egdf5ag4840g998egcb84e919c54a": ["My love, you were a caravan escort for three days, and you quit in the middle of your shift.", "dcf597c0-36c5-4c81-957a-6fe9fca50a68", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "08e9ec03-d795-64c1-2084-21247ed0f01c"], "hb639ae6dge1ebg4caeg9ffcg5aa4e579a2a3": ["You sound like your father.", "dd9178e7-1e3f-43bc-8a38-666dfcac7d0c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "06e356ed-02e7-f123-1e5e-e35df14873bf"], "h5d012d73g967cg4a20g9a68gdecfd1834897": ["Well, it was his caravan.", "dcf597c0-36c5-4c81-957a-6fe9fca50a68", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "2537cd59-69f6-37c3-40a5-c603cb767809"], "hd62f71ccg6a6fg4021g86f2g63e3e5c9b0ea": ["What will we do for work when we get to the city?", "dcf597c0-36c5-4c81-957a-6fe9fca50a68", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "4b63b948-7361-32f6-66a4-c3c83bd2aea8"], "h3b324342g8235g4eb9gb360gf7cd152f494b": ["Whatever we want!", "dd9178e7-1e3f-43bc-8a38-666dfcac7d0c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "1de23ac8-6733-df67-646d-930e0573b7e5"], "h54b396a4g3ea8g4676gaf70gbbadc245f3c8": ["I think I'd make a fine teacher. Or a baker. Or a butcher.", "dcf597c0-36c5-4c81-957a-6fe9fca50a68", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "b6bfbe15-c00b-85e1-c6bb-c2343b173e95"], "h012b7466g4ca1g4d76g81a2g65d3a735c704": ["A butcher? Really?", "dd9178e7-1e3f-43bc-8a38-666dfcac7d0c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "f3e18335-98a8-48ce-6576-3fa876112a79"], "hd59ae9c3g1d37g4570gbffbg459121c9c8e1": ["Sure. Blood excites me.", "dcf597c0-36c5-4c81-957a-6fe9fca50a68", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "69493db6-111a-f7d6-4005-8192cf7a2cfc"], "hc89c85bcg4dc4g4522g9883ga061153c9180": ["Erm... right.", "dd9178e7-1e3f-43bc-8a38-666dfcac7d0c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_YoungLover_AD_Shared.html", "d3f21827-f6b9-b760-c3db-04e0c3323025"]}